body_html: @rmlarsen Is there any way to see compiler parameters and what architecture it's using for this build, is it x86_64? Would appreciate any extra info on that, as I said, it's very hard to reproduce since everything is working great on my MacOS, but I assume that target architecture could be different. Maybe it's not a good idea to try to push using neon2sse from the beginning. Anyway, it's unlikely that TF Lite will be run at x86.
